trans-unit.source: Provides a translation function for a mapped property of the host control.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller en funktion för översättning för mappad egenskap i kontrollen värden.

trans-unit.source: The PropertyTranslator delegate is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap> class to implement property mapping between [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] and [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Delegaten PropertyTranslator används av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap>klassen för att implementera egenskapsmappning mellan [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] och [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)].</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Windows Forms and WPF Property Mapping](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [Windows Forms och WPF egenskapsmappning](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
